project:
Game by Rger Goulart for Magical Girl Game Jam 12 and Metroidvania Month 29.

Music by Ansimuz

Thank you for playing!
Press C/L1 for a short time intangible form.
Press Space/B for a rolling dodge.
Press Jump in the air for a second jump.
Hold jump in the air for a slowfall.
Press Jump in the air for a second jump.
Press C/L1 for a short time intangible form.
Hold down and press Jump for a rolling dodge.
Press Jump in the air for a second jump.
